items.name: Star Wars: Exodus Visual Encyclopedia
items.title: Star Wars: Exodus Visual Encyclopedia
items.headline: Welcome to the Star Wars: Exodus Visual Encyclopedia
items.desc:
Star Wars: Exodus is a roleplaying community that has been around since Feburary 14, 2003. However, before we formed Star Wars: Exodus we were on the Sony Star Wars Galaxies Roleplaying Forum, since roughly the year 1999 or 2000. The purpose of this site is to help members new and old remember, or get to know, the stories of the past. Furthermore, new stories are added as they are developed.

In all of the reading material that can be found at the Exodus boards, it is easy to get lost with the masses of information presented. So, as well as serving as a grounds for recording past and present stories, the Visual Encyclopedia also allows for the implementation of other story-enhancing features. Whether they be a personal character, or an entire galaxy-wide government, it is all here, in the Visual Encyclopedia.

items.name: Star Wars Battlefront Wiki
items.title: Star Wars Battlefront Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to Star Wars Battlefront Wiki!
items.desc:
Are you new to Star Wars Battlefront series, or a Veteran? No matter who you are and your role, we welcome you to the community! Learn about strategies to conquer maps; or if you are sneaky, feel free to learn about glitches from Bespin: Cloud City to Yavin 4: Temple! Discover some glitch or strategy that no one knows about? Give in your share! Our friendly staff will find a way to help you through your time with us, whether you are new to Wikia, or just need a social wiki to spend your time. We always have a set of watchful eyes for unpleasant personnel.

Due to a growing number of Mod community, we have our share, and trying our best to give you what we know from mods we have tried. Just want to find a fellow group of Battlefrontians to rely on to give hints, our wiki is the right place! Our different time zone Admin ensures a near 24/7 service to those that need help! But you are probably tired of these summery, go come to the website and find out for yourself! See you there!

items.name: Star Wars Games
items.title: Star Wars Games
items.headline: The force is strong at the Star Wars Game Wikia
items.desc: The Star Wars Games Wikia is a Wikia community dedicated to being the number one resource of everything related to Star War Games. These games include the popular Battlefront series, as well as the Knights of the Old Republic. Our community covers all the information related to the characters, the weapons, the stories, the levels, and whatever else is found within these games. Anybody is free to join and help make this Wikia a better resource.

items.name: Lego Star Wars Wiki
items.title: Lego Star Wars Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Lego Star Wars Wiki
items.desc:
Welcome to Lego Star Wars Wiki, a free online Lego Star Wars Information provider written collaboratively by its readers. This site is a Wiki meaning that anyone including you, can edit and contribute too!

The Lego Star Wars Wiki runs using the same software used by Wikipedia known as MediaWiki, and with the help of editors like you we aim to have pages on any LEGO Star Wars product and strive to be the best source for LEGO Star Wars information out there for LEGO fans of all ages!

items.name: SWRPEDIA - Second Life Star Wars Roleplay Wiki
items.title: SWRPEDIA - Second Life Star Wars Roleplay Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Second Life Star Wars Roleplay Wiki
items.desc: This wiki is about the Star Wars Role-play community that operates within the game Second Life. Anyone can create, edit, and search articles related to characters, factions, locations, combat systems, user-created items, role-play story-lines, and much more. It's open to all! Founded in 2008, the wiki has just over 1,500 pages covering the events within this entirely player created role-play community.
